Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:15.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:20.33,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:24.87,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:37.95,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:46.36,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:53.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:58.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:05.51,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:15.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:23.00,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:27.73,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:34.67,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:01:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After swim class, let's get something to eat at the Road House,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and then go see "Love Awakening!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! It's been so long since we've just gone out and {\i1}done{\i0} something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, give it some thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has been over two weeks now since Saint-Juste-sama passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Additionally, the Sorority members learned of what Miya-sama said;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}now that whole tradition has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, finally, summer vacation has arrived at Seiran Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am doing well, dear brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope to be able to write you a letter any day now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,36. Light of the Fireflies, Ablaze with Passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara-san, the doctor would like to take a look at how the affected area is progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please undress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara-san, please remove everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you'll be pretty busy during the summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can come in every other week then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You only got out of the hospital a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would be best to run some more detailed tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So then... I'm not going to make it, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, now, I didn't say anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it to me straight! I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I thought it might be serious, I'd have you back in the hospital until we knew for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Orihara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that Larry Duncan is pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we hop over to the Roxy for a quick drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the flowers to dry out....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako! There's somebody there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Up on the overpass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been just sitting there for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother, Kaoru-no-Kimi was....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear brother... Kaoru-no-Kimi was crying....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was as though all her deepest sorrows were finally risen to the surface....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if she were forced against her will by her own despair....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Indeed, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I saw then that there was another apart from myself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,who could not come to terms with Saint-Juste-sama's death....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One for whom the pain of sorrow runs deeper than I could ever know....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One whose grief is so strong... it is tearing her apart....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaoru-no-Kimi, whom I had always thought to be so strong, so unshakable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Kaoru-no-Kimi is crying now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are people born into this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And why do they even bother to go on living?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all going to die someday, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Joutou University, Department of Humanities and Cultural Studies....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a call for you while you were out earlier, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The caller was a Mr. Henmi Takehiko, from the University.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi Takehiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. He indicated that he wishes to speak with you about studying abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying abroad? Henmi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he an aquaintance of yours, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.... Yes, I know him well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then... about his appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise! You, turning down a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I have times when I just don't feel like drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so sudden, wasn't it.... About Rei-san....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She was an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I think I'll have one after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... Fukiko... the whole family.... Everyone is obsessed over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we never did a {\i1}thing{\i0} for that girl in her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the regret over that is coming back to haunt us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it acknowledgement of our sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She was our own child, even if she was born into an unfortunate life;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,yet we never tried to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that she has been taken away from us so early...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...we realize just how many things there were that we should have done for her, but didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As her brother... as her family!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever leave something undone that you'll regret later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave no regrets....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me! You know who I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were to go, too, no words of yours could ever make me forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?! What's with this "study abroad" business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving that serious thought as well....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone from the Seiran basketball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Basketball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Misonoo speaking....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and we're in a pinch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a match starting at six, and she hasn't shown up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No one at her home knows anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They say she hasn't come home since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother... Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired, Rei. So tired....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was stopping by to visit Saint-Juste-sama's room....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I must seem like an idiot, I know....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Saint-Juste-sama's room any more....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known that someone else would be living there now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama would know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if something had happened to Kaoru-no-Kimi, Saint-Juste-sama would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The elevator had already reached the fifth floor; I was just about to ring the bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then it finally occured to me that she wasn't there any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, what's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about Orihara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't show up for a basketball match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They say she hasn't been home since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in! Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to Henmi's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to talk to him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,About Orihara-kun. About her condition, in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? To my brother? About Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Anything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why would Henmi-san want to know about Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you never knew, Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi Takehiko is the one person she needs more than anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,About a year or so ago, those two were a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For certain reasons, they broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, it isn't as though they hate or even dislike one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, they share a bond in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it seems to me, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I never knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I love you, I must leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I love you, I must forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must even make myself forget that there was ever anything to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that, because I love you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to die while I lived on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I would go on living...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I would do my best to go on living with what little time I have left, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You never troubled anyone; you always kept to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You lived your life without regrets. So beautiful... so pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Rei! To think that you would die before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your courage never falter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you ever afraid of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When you felt lonely, so very lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...did you ever find yourself not knowing what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has been coping as best they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No one realized just how much of a shock Rei's death was to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you lend me the car keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother, the love between you and Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takashi-san said that it came to an end over a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said that you had parted ways, though you were still bound to one another in your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wouldn't tell me the reason why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... it must have been a sorrowful romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mightn't Kaoru-no-Kimi have experienced such a love long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd had a feeling that might have been the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you borrow an umbrella from someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, yes. From my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, my dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My silent, strong, kind brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Henmi... Takehiko....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact that's a person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a man's name, has suddenly been made a little more real to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that you had to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this was where you had to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! Don't trouble yourself over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting this past year, waiting the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting until you needed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before, I'll live my life alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! It's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Takehiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you come to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here, to the place where we parted for the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, ever since that time when we parted here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...my heart has remained here, at this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That part of me that said "I love you" has lingered on, here, in this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, too... Your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was left behind here, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. I have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have forgotten all about those sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So look at me. I want you to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want you to forget me, I want you to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? I could never bring you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you could love me the way I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...the more we felt for one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...the bleaker your future would become, because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so... and so... I must forget you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me that you need me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the wonderful times that we had were precious moments for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rain let up before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sorry to trouble you, but is this the Orihara residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, what about breakfast? Won't you be having something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Yes, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right back? Where are you off to so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that she's returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The folks at her home told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She came back late last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but she's headed off to the morning basketball practice, up at the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't true, there was no early morning practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I wish that Saint-Juste-sama were here..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps that's what I was saying to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you remembered that it was Rei's favorite place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She used to skip class here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... everyone has been worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The basketball club... Ichinomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Henmi-san, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... I'd totally forgotten about the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I heard from Ichinomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:21:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...about Henmi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all over now, but... would you like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when Rei and I had first become friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ichinomiya-san came over to Rei's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-san introduced Henmi-san to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in love the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Those dark brown eyes sparkled so enchantingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We went various places...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... one time the two of us rode the carousel together...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It made for a splendid memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But... we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder whether you should know the reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery, you see. They had to remove one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When a relapse occurs within five years... there isn't really any hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.25,0:23:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:13.71,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.71,0:24:19.18,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:24.79,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:30.26,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.00,0:24:36.54,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:42.01,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:44.74,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.74,0:24:47.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.55,0:24:49.95,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.95,0:24:55.22,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.37,0:25:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako knows that Henmi is her true brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.78,0:25:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi and Misonoo meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.07,0:25:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,after more than ten years to reaffirm the love of a parent and a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So begins their journey forth into a new day... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.43,0:25:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode: Merry-Go-Round
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.22,0:25:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother... there is no end to my tears...
